Yoooo, zup? :D

Well, gotta say that i beat every level and got every achievement in something like 1 hour. 
It's kinda weird but it's just like that. Anyways it's really fun to play, that's for sure.
You will understand it when you start playing. I found some achievements kinda funny, i mean, the way you get them.


PROS:
- Not boring at all;
- Good value;
- Nice artwork;
- Nice puzzles;
- Variety of levels;
- Way more levels than the previous Zup's;

After you play this game you'll want to buy the other Zup's as i did.
I hope they keep doing more games like this, i'm ready for Zup 6,7,8,9 and Infinite :D

MY RATING: 10/10


